title: Formlabs on building the Form 2 3D printer from the ground up
text:
Formlabs on building the Form 2 3D printer from the ground up 5 October 2015 Expand Formlabs ' Co-founder and TCT Show + Personalize 2015 keynote speaker, Max Lobovsky talks to TCT about how the company designed the new Form 2 desktop stereolithography machine from the ground up to create the machine they always wanted to build. With this second generation 3D printer, Formlabs are bringing bigger, smarter and more powerful 3D printing to the professional community. 
To keep up-to-date on all the latest videos from TCT Show make sure you subscribe to our YouTube channel . Tags
